{"tid":418993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人將奪80命倫敦嘅大火樓視為觀光景點「朝聖」","createTime":"2017-09-30T05:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T10:30:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"7c95f73c32d09d9a42abea7ab813a0b52a145307","tid":418993,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170930/large/1506743667_5a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170930%2Flarge%2F1506743667_5a1e.jpg&h=f90e7194&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》與《太陽報》報道，有倫敦民眾在facebook貼文，指看到有旅遊巴士載着一群中國遊客來到Grenfell Tower，他曾詢問該旅遊巴士司機有關這團人的來歷，獲覆他們是安全衞生專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。該民眾表示，他認為網上已經夠多關於Grenfell Tower的報道與照片，根本不需要跑到現場拍照，他更不希望Grenfell Tower變成一個觀光景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i1.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article11259000.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/photographs-at-site-of-Grenfell.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle11259000.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615b%2Fphotographs-at-site-of-Grenfell.jpg&h=e65ccdc7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n報道又指出，許多民眾也在大樓現場貼紙條，呼籲大家不要來這裏自拍，不要把自己的快樂好奇，建築在受害者與罹難者的痛苦上。許多英國網友看到這群中國遊客的行徑，也紛紛大罵：「不尊重、沒品」、「來這邊請尊重，不是來拍照的」、「遣返導遊，自拍不能無底線」、「真的是太惡心了！」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/nintchdbpict000356896947.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fnintchdbpict000356896947.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D960&h=2c993e53&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n而承包這個中國旅行團的旅巴公司「BM Coaches」事後也致歉，涉事的導遊已被遣返中國，並稱當天接載遊客的旅遊巴司機也遭停職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170930/57273605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170930%2F57273605&d=AfmLICu2aAgMYMPP%2B1E3umi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3c09ce96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170930%2F57273605&h=ddbb454a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170930/57273605</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/4573979/chinese-tourists-grenfell-tower-fire/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fnews%2F4573979%2Fchinese-tourists-grenfell-tower-fire%2F&d=AfmLICu2aAgMYMPP%2B1E3umi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1d0ccb9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/4573979/chinese-tourists-grenfell-tower-fire/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4932518/Chinese-guide-sent-home-taking-tourists-Grenfell.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-4932518%2FChinese-guide-sent-home-taking-tourists-Grenfell.html&d=AfmLICu2aAgMYMPP%2B1E3umi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3b5592ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4932518/Chinese-guide-sent-home-taking-tourists-Grenfell.html</a>"},{"pid":"432919a27c78021f423088afc530f01eb89be26d","tid":418993,"uid":21979,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"旅遊地點又唔係司機決定<br />\n炒佢做咩..."},{"pid":"66db7af527b736639b13c4ff17e2d04ac296ad74","tid":418993,"uid":8009,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那有咩資格笑人<br />\n啊佢地係數字"},{"pid":"5e81911384aca77b67f2832352157f515fd19cf4","tid":418993,"uid":1886,"like":